c","tid":1782453,"uid":20690,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T03:43:16.000Z","msg":"真相，唉，周同學，真相是：魚香茄子並沒有魚，記住了。<br />\n有冇人可以解下夕爺咩意思？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T03:50:51.000Z","msg":"周同學嘅朋友憶述，係出事前一排，周同學先知道原來魚香茄子係冇魚嘅"},{"pid":"9b6d22598e15dd365cb05d5c66437fe61ae2ec25","tid":1782453,"uid":321450,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"30aa383e68e8e3f65f5e94e9e079e9a7262e2cac","tid":1782453,"uid":20690,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T03:43:16.000Z","msg":"真相，唉，周同學，真相是：魚香茄子並沒有魚，記住了。<br />\n有冇人可以解下夕爺咩意思？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T03:51:22.000Z","msg":"魚香茄子沒有魚，之前周同學個朋友講佢最近先知道。<br />\n<br />\n我估夕爺既意思係。周同學俾魚香茄子呢個名呃左咁耐，到臨終前無耐先知道真相，證明周同學性格單純，暗喻呢個香港好多真相都係名不符實，可惜周同學已經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57049ebae2b0fdd176a3d296c0b290ec24e29329","tid":1782453,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T04:03:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7d2e2d5d8ce6b7aad32118f3e118cd9ee83868f","tid":1782453,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T04:11:00.000Z","msg":"睇完篇文忍唔住又喊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50bcb3a4f078d35761a3a3ce94e38aec728d3d9b","tid":1782453,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T04:18:57.000Z","msg":"好文賞評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff06276a080ade7a8c81b6c11c60e65089e899cd","tid":1782453,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T04:20:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">周同學，真相是：魚香茄子並沒有魚，記住了。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n這句是何等唏噓<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24e94183496921efc8b1309ed9ea8d1c43ee823d","tid":1782453,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T04:44:11.000Z","msg":"乜原來無魚架，有冇人講下魚香茄子係有乜嘢食材？"},{"pid":"b95eb2f7f5b0f56a2af9c86182a132b356310933","tid":1782453,"uid":272652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T05:09:04.000Z","msg":"夕爺，周同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f265a0d931ae0f61073f01e84f2cbaf2dbe9743","tid":1782453,"uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"24e94183496921efc8b1309ed9ea8d1c43ee823d","tid":1782453,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T04:44:11.000Z","msg":"乜原來無魚架，有冇人講下魚香茄子係有乜嘢食材？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T17:51:27.000Z","msg":"魚香茄子是一道常見川菜。魚香是川菜主要傳統味型之一。成菜具有魚香味，但其味並不來自魚，而是泡红辣椒、葱、薑、蒜、糖、鹽、醬油等調味品調制而成。此法源出於四川民間獨具特色的烹魚調味方法，而今已廣泛用於川味的熟菜中，具有鹹、酸、甜、辣、香、鮮和濃郁的葱、薑、蒜味的特色。<br />\n<br />\n一般食材<br />\n茄子 <br />\n豬肉 <br />\n蒜頭 <br />\n紹興酒 <br />\n鹽 <br />\n黑胡椒 <br />\n豆瓣醬 <br />\n豉油 <br />\n醋 <br />\n砂糖 <br />\n清水"},{"pid":"2be485c5dbbcb04f7fc40a2ffe92340ad2dc1ee8","tid":1782453,"uid":32586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f265a0d931ae0f61073f01e84f2cbaf2dbe9743","tid":1782453,"uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"24e94183496921efc8b1309ed9ea8d1c43ee823d","tid":1782453,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T04:44:11.000Z","msg":"乜原來無魚架，有冇人講下魚香茄子係有乜嘢食材？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T17:51:27.000Z","msg":"魚香茄子是一道常見川菜。魚香是川菜主要傳統味型之一。成菜具有魚香味，但其味並不來自魚，而是泡红辣椒、葱、薑、蒜、糖、鹽、醬油等調味品調制而成。此法源出於四川民間獨具特色的烹魚調味方法，而今已廣泛用於川味的熟菜中，具有鹹、酸、甜、辣、香、鮮和濃郁的葱、薑、蒜味的特色。<br />\n<br />\n一般食材<br />\n茄子 <br />\n豬肉 <br />\n蒜頭 <br />\n紹興酒 <br />\n鹽 <br />\n黑胡椒 <br />\n豆瓣醬 <br />\n豉油 <br />\n醋 <br />\n砂糖 <br />\n清水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T17:56:54.000Z","msg":"正宗嘅冇 但有啲鋪會落鹹魚"},{"pid":"2f680b980ce6eb9a75da4286175